strings.suggest.checklist.brief: Bẹrẹ atokọ iṣẹ ṣiṣe: jẹrisi awọn irinṣẹ pataki ti fi sori ẹrọ ati kọ ṣiṣe.
strings.suggest.checklist.extensive: Atokọ iṣẹ ṣiṣe ti o pọju: idojukọ lori awọn igbesẹ ti o mu iyara ati ṣiṣe dara si.
strings.suggest.memory.low: Iranti ọfẹ kekere: sunmọ awọn ohun elo ti ko lo tabi tun bẹrẹ si Ramu ọfẹ.
strings.suggest.memory.veryHigh: Lilo Ramu>= 90%: awọn ohun elo ti o wuwo sunmọ, duro duro, tabi pọ si Ramu eto.
strings.suggest.memory.high: Lilo Ramu>= 80%: ronu pipade awọn ohun elo tabi jijẹ Ramu ti eyi ba wọpọ.
strings.suggest.memory.reserve: Jeki 20% Ramu ọfẹ fun kaṣe ati awọn iṣẹ-ṣiṣe OS; 10% ni o kere julọ lati yago fun awọn idinku.
strings.suggest.cpu.high: Iwọn giga CPU: ṣayẹwo Oluṣakoso Iṣẹ-ṣiṣe fun awọn ilana ti o wuwo.
strings.suggest.internet.failed: Ṣiṣayẹwo Intanẹẹti kuna: jẹrisi asopọ rẹ tabi ogiriina.
strings.suggest.internet.latency: Lairi intanẹẹti giga: gbiyanju yiyipada awọn nẹtiwọọki tabi tun olulana bẹrẹ.
strings.suggest.os.updates: macOS imudojuiwọn wa: fi sori ẹrọ awọn imudojuiwọn titun.
strings.suggest.gpu.full: Ṣiṣe awọn iwadii kikun lati ni _TOK_4__ ati awọn alaye ilana.
strings.suggest.ide.cap: JetBrains IDE fila ti ri: mu IDE iwọn okiti pọ si ti iṣẹ ṣiṣe ba lọra.
strings.suggest.wifi.weak: Alailagbara Wi-Fi (<60%): sunmo olulana tabi yipada si Ethernet.
strings.suggest.wifi.weakRssi: Alailagbara Wi-Fi (RSSI kekere): sunmo olulana tabi yipada si Ethernet.
strings.suggest.power.plan: A ko ṣeto ero agbara si iṣẹ giga: yipada si Ti o dara julọ / Iṣe giga lakoko ifaminsi tabi ile.
strings.suggest.vscode.extensions: VS Code: mu awọn amugbooro ti ko lo ati yọkuro awọn folda kikọ/jade lati wiwo faili ati wiwa.
strings.suggest.jetbrains.tune: JetBrains IDEs: mu awọn afikun ti a ko lo, yọkuro iṣẹjade kikọ lati titọka, ati gbe iwọn okiti soke ti o ba nilo.
strings.suggest.vs.parallel: Visual Studio: jẹ ki awọn iṣẹ akanṣe ti o jọra ṣiṣẹ ati gbejade awọn iṣẹ akanṣe lati dinku akoko fifuye ojutu.
strings.suggest.xcode.derived: Xcode: nu DerivedData nigba titọka tabi kọ awọn akoko iwasoke.
strings.suggest.android.accel: Android Studio: mu imudara ohun elo emulator ṣiṣẹ ki o tọju kaṣe Gradle sori ibi ipamọ iyara.
strings.suggest.node.lts: Node.js: lo itusilẹ LTS tuntun ki o tọju awọn igbẹkẹle iṣẹ akanṣe lori ibi ipamọ SSD.
strings.suggest.ts.incremental: TypeScript: jẹ ki awọn idasile ti o pọ sii tabi awọn itọkasi iṣẹ akanṣe fun awọn koodu koodu nla.
strings.suggest.python.venv: Python: lo awọn agbegbe foju lati jẹ ki awọn fifi sori ẹrọ ya sọtọ ati yara.
strings.suggest.java.lts: Java: lo LTS JDK lọwọlọwọ ki o mu awọn caches kọ (Gradle/Maven) fun awọn atunṣeto yiyara.
strings.suggest.docker.windows: Docker Ojú-iṣẹ (Windows): lo WSL2 backend ati tune CPU/Ramu ifilelẹ lọ fun iṣẹ ṣiṣe rẹ.
strings.suggest.docker.mac: Docker Ojú-iṣẹ (macOS): tune CPU/Ramu ifilelẹ lọ ati pinpin faili (VirtioFS ti o ba wa).
strings.checklist.osDrivers: Ṣe imudojuiwọn OS ati awọn awakọ ẹrọ (GPU, chipset, Wi-Fi/LAN) si awọn ẹya iduroṣinṣin tuntun.
strings.checklist.powerPlan: Lo iṣẹ ṣiṣe giga / ero agbara iṣẹ ṣiṣe to dara julọ lakoko ifaminsi tabi kikọ.
strings.checklist.startupApps: Pa tabi gee awọn ohun elo ibẹrẹ ati awọn iṣẹ abẹlẹ ti o ko lo.
strings.checklist.diskSpace: Jeki o kere ju 20% aaye disk ọfẹ; ṣiṣe afọmọ disk ati yọ awọn faili iwọn otutu ti o tobi kuro.
strings.checklist.ssd: O fẹ ibi ipamọ SSD fun awọn iṣẹ akanṣe; yago fun eru duro lori o lọra ita drives.
strings.checklist.visualEffects: Din wiwo ipa / awọn ohun idanilaraya fun snappier UI.
strings.checklist.antivirus: Yasọtọ awọn folda iṣẹ akanṣe (node_modules, kọ, dist) lati ọlọjẹ ọlọjẹ akoko gidi.
strings.checklist.wifi: Lo Ethernet tabi lagbara 5GHz Wi-Fi; imudojuiwọn famuwia olulana ati atunbere lorekore.
strings.checklist.dns: Ṣeto DNS si olupese ti o yara ati rii daju idaduro kekere fun awọn igbasilẹ akojọpọ.
strings.checklist.browser: Ṣe idinwo awọn taabu aṣawakiri ati sunmọ awọn ohun elo wuwo lakoko awọn kikọ.
strings.checklist.hwAccel: Mu ohun elo isare ṣiṣẹ nibiti atilẹyin (alawakiri/IDE).
strings.checklist.cliTools: Jeki awọn irinṣẹ CLI di oni (Node.js, npm, Git, Docker, Java).
strings.checklist.reboot: Atunbere lẹhin awọn imudojuiwọn pataki lati ko awọn ilana ati awọn titiipa kuro.
strings.note.speedtest.unavailable: Ko si awọn orisun iyara to dahun.
strings.note.speedtest.captive: Awari ọna abawọle igbekun; iyara dina.
